Description=YADIFA is a lightweight authoritative Name Server with DNSSEC capabilities.${Newline} Developed by the passionate people behind the .eu top-level domain, YADIFA${Newline} has been built from scratch to face today's DNS challenges, with no${Newline} compromise on security, speed and stability, to offer a better and safer${Newline} Internet experience. YADIFA has a simple configuration syntax and can handle${Newline} more queries per second while maintaining one of the lowest memory footprints${Newline} in the industry. YADIFA also has one of the fastest zone file load times${Newline} ever recorded on a name server.
